------------------------------------
Changing the colour of notes windows
------------------------------------

You can make these notes easier on the eye by changing their colour:

    Right-click in the body of this window and select [Colours...]

    Click on the [Variables] tab.

    From the [Color Element] drop-down, select [Character Vector] or click
    in the [CharVector - ...] window.

    Choose Foreground and Background colours to taste.

    Click on [OK].

